title: Dessert Masters
overview: This mouth-watering series will see 10 of Australia's most decorated pastry chefs, chocolate connoisseurs and baking experts whisk it all to be named Australia's first ever Dessert Master.Juggernaut judges Melissa Leong and Amaury Guichon are ready and raring to taste their way through what will be some of the most inventive and irresistible desserts Australia has ever seen.
